			<p class="w3-margin-right"><small>
			Sandell, Ryan P. 2020, Gothic – Morphology, Part 4: Verbal Inflection. In Saverio Dalpedri, Götz Keydana, and Stavros Skopeteas (eds.), <i>Glottothèque: Ancient Indo-European Grammars online</i> (electronic resource). Göttingen: University of Göttingen. DOI: https://doi.org/10.5446/49506.
