			<br>Uppsala University Library. No date. <a href="https://ub.uu.se/about-the-library/exhibitions/codex-argenteus/" style="color:#0000FF;" target="_blank"><i>Codex Argenteus</i></a>. (Accessed 2021-07-05.)
			<br>
			<br>See also a digitized version of the Gothic Bible at the <a href="http://www.wulfila.be/gothic/browse/" style="color:#0000FF;" target="_blank">Wulfila Project</a>, see also a selection of available texts on <a href="http://lexicity.com/resources/gothic/texts/" style="color:#0000FF;" target="_blank">Lexicity 2016</a>.
